metadata.name: Alpha House: Squad On Stage #1/4
metadata.description:
Grab your crew, step up on stage, sit your ass down on your private couch, and let the drinks come to you. The VIP experience of a lifetime.

By acquiring this NFT, it grants you the following for Alpha House:  
- 8 VIP tickets included  
- 1 free drink ticket per guest  
- Seating on stage with couches, chairs, and coffee tables  
- Private drink runners  
- Backstage access to chill area  
- 4/4 Limited edition NFT

Alpha House  
An IRL Web3 Experience  
First Avenue Mainroom  
May 19th, 2022 at 8pm CT
